quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,"Nde …ďe nji'oyta (le…ďte) …óen ka …ďadii, j'eece yeddu…ďe …ďen suni j'eece he'efer…ďe, […ďe] mbi'anee : "Ko …óuum …óoo woni ko …óa…ď…ďatno…óon"."
  67,28,"Maaku : "Yeetee kam, si Allah ∆īettitii kam miin e wonndii…ďe am maa o yurmaama min, ko hommbo da…óndata he'efer…ďe …ďeen lepte mu'usuu…óe?""
  67,29,"Maaku : "Ko KaŇčko Joom hinaraŇčke oon. Min ngooŇč…óinii mo, ko e makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde nganndon ko hommbo woni e majjere …ďanngunde"."
  67,30,"Maaku : "njeewtee kam , si ndiyam mon …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilat…óam?""
  68,1,"Nuun. Mi woo…óndirii ku…óol e ko …ďe mbinndirta ko!"
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joommaa o, kaangaa…óo."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodani-ma njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, ha…óa e jikku maw…óo."
  68,5,"Aray nde nji'aa, …ďe nji'a kam…ďe kadi"
  68,6,"ko hombo e mon woni kaangaa…óo oon."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joommaa …ďuri anndude majju…óo on laawol makko ngol, ko KaŇčko kadi …ďuri anndude feew…ďe …ďe."
  68,8,"Wota a tefto yeddoo…ďe …ďen."
  68,9,"He…ďe nji…ói si a newantono (…ďe), …ďe newano-(maa)."
  68,10,"Wota a tefto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondugol, koy…óo."
  68,11,"…óuu…óu…óo √Īo'ougol, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol ba…ódi."
  68,12,"…óuu…óu…óo ka…ógol mo∆ī∆īere, jaggitoowo, bakkodi'…óo."
  68,13,"yo'ora-…ďerndeejo e hoore …óum, ke…ďiraa…óo nii(.…ďiy jina)."
  68,14,"fii o wonii joom jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe."
  68,15,"Si aayeeje amen …óeen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: "Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe"."